# Working with gitban

New here? Read **`.gitban/README.md`** first — the fastest path to seeing the
board and doing work. For the full workflow (how PRDs, ADRs, and design docs
become sprints and get executed), see **`.gitban/docs/development-lifecycle.md`**.

# Project-specific instructions

<!--
  Add your project's own instructions here. Examples of what fits well in
  this section:
    - Which test runner / venv resolver to use
    - Local commit-style rules (e.g. no co-author tags, no emoji)
